###Calculating the violatality of a stock:
In [40]:
tesla['returns']= ((tesla['Open']/tesla['Open'].shift(1))-1)
ford['returns']= ((ford['Open']/ford['Open'].shift(1))-1)
gm['returns']= ((gm['Open']/gm['Open'].shift(1))-1)
